## 1) Download Splunk Enterprise (router 10.9.0.11)
1. On the router, download the appropriate Splunk Enterprise package (Linux .rpm/.deb or tar.gz) from https://www.splunk.com (use the version matching your OS).
   Example:
   ```bash
   wget <splunk-enterprise-wget-link>


#Install package:
sudo dpkg -i splunk_package_name.deb

#RHEL/CentOS (rpm):
sudo rpm -ivh splunk_package_name.rpm

#Tar:
tar -xvf splunk_package_name.tgz -C /opt



